 pregnant!"],[5280,5442,"You are not a monster, Bash."],[5459,5651,"Come with me and our baby."],[5751,5839,"I'm so sorry."],[6018,6106,"I'm coming, baby."],[6122,6189,"I'm coming."],[6256,6418,"You're not going anywhere, bitch!"],[6477,6527,"Kill him."],[6731,6781,"No!"],[6827,6877,"No..."],[7140,7240,"Andy, please."],[7257,7340,"Bash..."]],"56":[[87,154,"Wait!"],[166,233,"Andy, wait!"],[429,550,"You bitch!"],[550,617,"Police!"],[617,696,"Wait!"],[763,804,"Right here."],[804,846,"These guys."],[846,930,"- Right here. - Yeah."],[1013,1113,"Put your fucking hands"],[1113,1213,"behind your back."],[1288,1351,"Fuck you!"],[1455,1518,"Let's go."],[1626,1697,"Bash!"],[1889,2052,"No... no no no no..."],[2548,2648,"Matty, you should know that"],[2648,2786,"all that I care about is"],[2786,2948,"your brother's safety."],[2969,3073,"That might be true,"],[3107,3244,"but his dreams are a lot bigger than"],[3244,3311,"safety."],[3453,3541,"I think you should go."],[3641,3753,"I need some time with my brother."],[4391,4479,"We have Sebastian's"],[4479,4608,"belongings that were found on him."],[4696,4746,"Thanks."],[5488,5613,"An engagement ring?"],[5626,5759,"My little brother was going to"],[5759,5880,"propose to Olivia?"],[6143,6314,"They say I finally"],[6360,6527,"get to go home tomorrow, honey."],[6602,6760,"And then I can finally get to know"],[6760,6877,"that special"],[6898,6973,"Bash."],[7282,7378,"About that, mom..."],[7553,7707,"I don't think that he wants..."],[7766,7832,"me..."],[7937,8053,"or our baby."],[8099,8220,"What are you talking about?"],[8458,8504,"Oh..."],[8533,8596,"Olivia."],[8729,8842,"You don't know, do you?"]],"57":[[513,621,"Is this her mom's ring?"],[1121,1230,"If you're going to give her this..."],[1422,1530,"I think you should give her this, too."],[2302,2402,"This is Mom's ring."],[2435,2577,"She would want Olivia to have it."],[2669,2781,"Look, man, I've been really..."],[2936,3003,"selfish."],[3057,3190,"And after I saw the ring,"],[3211,327